# Lua API integration

## HUD
```lua
local hud = LuaHUD.new()

hud:hotbar {
   pos = {x = 42, y = 84},
   texture = "default_hotbar.png",
   slots = 8,
}

openminer:player():set_hud(hud)
```
## World
```lua
openminer:get_block(pos)
openminer:get_meta(pos)
openminer:get_inventory(pos)
```
